Take the apple on the right from the sink.
Turn around, go to the counter over the dishwasher.
Put the apple on the right of the statue and in front of the salt.
Stay at the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Stay at the counter.
Cut the apple into pieces.
Turn around, go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into pieces.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn around, go to the counter over the dishwasher.
Put the piece of apple to the left of the other cut apple.

Cut the apple on the counter with the knife.
Turn around and face the sink.
Cut the apple that is inside of the sink.
Place the knife into the sink.
Pick up an apple slice out of the sink.
Turn around to face the counter.
Place the apple slice the the left of the previously sliced apple.

Pick up the green apple in the right side of the sink basin.

Look up at the green apple on the counter.
Cut the apple that is to the left of the statue into three pieces with the butter knife.
Turn right and walk over to the sink.
Use the butter knife to slice the lime in the sink into three pieces.

Pick up middle lime slice out of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the section of counter above the dish washer.
Put the slice of lime onto the counter to the left of the sliced apple.

take an apple from the sink.
